Calculate the mean weight in stock and catch

Source: R/FLStock.R
meanwt.Rd

Average weight in the stock numbers or catch-at-age.

Usage

meanwt(object)

meanwtCatch(object)

Arguments

object

An age-structured FLStock object

Value

An FLQuant object

See also

FLComp

Author

The FLR Team

data(ple4)
